Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:25.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,It's a beautiful day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.69,0:00:31.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.07,0:00:34.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, are you still sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:38.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko, get my cell for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:47.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello, is this the police?\NI'd like to report a trespasser.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:57.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What grows on its own? Hmm, what is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.81,0:01:00.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one more{\i0}\N{\i1}chance. Never never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One more chance, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance. Never give up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.73,0:01:12.41,Main,,0,0,0,,BAKA and TEST\N-Summon the Beasts-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Nice to encounter you,"{\i0}\N{\i1}that one's too easy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:19.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's only one answer{\i0}\N{\i1}that I decided on at the start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.04,0:01:21.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart fluttered. Will I pass?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:24.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't panic whether{\i0}\N{\i1}it's a matter of love or war{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sigh as I cram all night long{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:29.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a genius dreamer inside of me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.46,0:01:32.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It'd be nice if everything I wanted came true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:34.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pay no mind to other people's worlds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.55,0:01:37.14,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll definitely be waiting right here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.81,0:01:46.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perfect-area, I can hear someone wishing for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:47.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah! Ear! Ear!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why? We just keep missing each other{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:53.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you came to me for advice, it'd go like{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.41,0:01:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"So, friends?" "Yes, friends."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:57.99,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a sad 0 points.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.99,0:02:01.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No! Do it again! Rewrite it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.29,0:02:03.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1} I'm serious, one{\i0}\N{\i1}more chance please{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You know, there's a future{\i0}\N{\i1}more wonderful than now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:14.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make it more wonderful than{\i0}\N{\i1}now... my life, my life, my life{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"Sweat"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is that? I've never\Nseen that book before in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.44,Main,,0,0,0,,It was hidden under the false\Nbottom in the third drawer of your desk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,with a reference book cover on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:35.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello? What's the matter? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:38.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:41.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, just burn it and I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.95,0:02:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait. You wouldn't punish me like\Nthat if you were planning to forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, I won't forgive you even if you burn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.92,0:02:49.25,Main,,0,0,0,,So you want it burned either way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:53.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.13,0:02:55.88,Main,,0,0,0,,So what do you want so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.47,0:02:58.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:03.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That's... a premium ticket for\NKisaragi Grand Park? Why do you have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,--A kind person gave it to me with good intentions.\N--Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,--Akihisa is pretty much the only one I know who had one.\N--It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:14.69,Main,,0,0,0,,The special event, Wedding Experience...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.07,0:03:17.16,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Akihisa Yoshii"\N"Blocking number"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.45,MainTop,,0,0,0,,Hello? Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:20.78,MainTop,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.78,0:03:23.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Who is this?! What?! Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:25.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go, Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:25.96,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.41,Main,,0,0,0,,You lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.41,0:03:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,I never promised anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.25,0:03:33.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You promised that you'd go\Nout with me if you lost the ST War.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Then you pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.59,0:03:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You swore that if you broke the\Npromise, you'd marry me right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that different from what we promised?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:45.39,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Episode 7"\N"Me, Shouko, and Kisaragi Grand Park"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:48.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! That damn Akihisa!{\i0}\N{\i1}He'll definitely pay for thi--{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ow, ow, ow... Stop it, Shouko!\N--All the couples are arm in arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.07,0:03:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,No one else is using an arm lock\Nto keep the other from running!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello! Welcome to Kisaragi Grand Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.33,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Yuuji Sakamoto" "Super Idiot"\N"Akihisa Yoshii"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:07.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Beep"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Akihisa. This sure is an\Namusing little trick you're pulling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.21,0:04:14.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.63,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.63,0:04:18.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.89,Main,,0,0,0,,You too?! What's the\Nmeaning of this, Hideyoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:31.77,Main,,0,0,0,,What're you talking about? I'm a\Nstaff member at Kisaragi Grand Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.77,0:04:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,I have no connection to\Nthis acquaintance you speak of.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:38.11,Main,,0,0,0,,If you insist on playing innocent, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.24,0:04:38.90,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Yuuji Sakamoto" "Hideyoshi Kinoshita"\N"Hideyoshi Kinoshita"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Oops, my hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it really necessary to go that far over this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.83,0:04:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:48.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you have the invitation ticket?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:48.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:49.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kisaragi Grand Park"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,"Kisaragi Grand Park"\NWhoa! This is a premium ticket for a special event!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Alpha calling Bravo. I've confirmed the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.13,0:04:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Code 70. We're moving onto Operation\NWedding. Make sure to take them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:03.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that violent communication about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Please pay no mind.\NIt has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,You were clearly talking about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:11.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's take a souvenir\Npicture, our special service.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:15.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like you can't hide your\Ninstinctive habits, huh, Muttsulini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... you're naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't do it again so forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:34.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. We'll continue this in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,I said I won't do it again! I don't have\Nthe slightest interest in your underwear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:45.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahhhh! That's so unfair! My temples are...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:46.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:48.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"We're getting married."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What's this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's our free service.\NWe added a special design to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,This photo will be displayed in the park's\Nphoto studio to commemorate your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.69,0:06:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling shy, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,I see nothing in this\Npicture for me to feel shy about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah! Look! Look, Ryuuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's have them take our picture, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.58,0:06:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Riko. Hey, buddy, you over there.\NWe'll let you take our picture, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:20.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I am very sorry, but this is a special\Nservice only for premium ticket holders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! What's the problem\Nwith taking just one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.09,Main,,0,0,0,,We're customers, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.05,Main,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Tenjo{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be better advertising\Nif you took a picture of us
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,instead of those boring brats? Well?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Tenge{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:31.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"{\i1}Yuiga{\i0}"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:37.44,Main,,0,0,0,,He's right. Isn't Ryuuta twice\Nas cool as that high school kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.40,0:06:39.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:40.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:43.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Those two bad-mouthed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't get bothered over something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:48.07,Main,,0,0,0,,If you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Just take the same kind of picture of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:55.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. If you insist... Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay. Please put your hand here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, squeeze hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:03.59,Main,,0,0,0,,"We're getting married."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:05.51,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You told us to take the same picture, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:10.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna strangle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:11.93,Main,,0,0,0,,This is bad! The burger head snapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.93,0:07:14.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you mocking me, you brats?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:20.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Looks like... this is gonna be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:29.12,Main,,0,0,0,,How did they sneak in here to begin with?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling shy, Yuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.28,0:07:34.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What man would feel shy\Nwhen his joints are being locked?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.95,Main,,0,0,0,,But couples are walking arm in arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.42,Main,,0,0,0,,This position wouldn't make\Nus look like a couple, would it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hi there, you lovey-dovey couple over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:45.17,Main,,0,0,0,,See? We look like a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:47.38,Main,,0,0,0,,There's clearly something\Nwrong with her, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Fee the fox! I'll introduce\Nyou to a very interesting attraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:56.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I saw Akihisa out on a date with\Na female college student earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Yoshii was? Where did you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:02.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you working here, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:12.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Fee the fox! I'll introduce\Nyou to a very interesting attraction!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:18.12,Main,,0,0,0,,If you wanna play innocent, that's\Nfine by me. Tell me your recommendation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:22.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay! My recommendation is the\Nhaunted house you see over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:26.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Shouko, we'll go\Nsomewhere {\i1}besides {\i0}the haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:29.72,Main,,0,0,0,,P-Please wait! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you guys have gone\Nand set something up for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Please! Go to the haunted house, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.31,0:08:39.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Stop right there, Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:44.82,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm Noin! I'm not going to\Nlet you cause Fee trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.82,0:08:47.78,Main,,0,0,0,,That getup is messed up in the head, Akihisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:50.36,Main,,0,0,0,,How rude! Which part is messed up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.36,0:08:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji, Noin is the absentminded one, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:56.54,Main,,0,0,0,,No fox would be so absentminded\Nas to have his head on backwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:59.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! You're wearing the\Nhead the other way around!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:02.08,Main,,0,0,0,,What?! Shoot! No wonder\NI couldn't see the front.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:05.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Fix it quick or Sakamoto will figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:09.59,Main,,0,0,0,,They really still think that\Nthey can keep us in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,By the way, Akihisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.18,Main,,0,0,0,,is your date with that female\Ncollege student over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.85,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii... I heard that you went on a date
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:24.56,Main,,0,0,0,,while we were carrying out our important plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.56,0:09:26.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you talking about, Himeji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,"Sending Mail"\N"Mizuki" "Minami"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:27.69,Main,,0,0,0,,"Mail Sent"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:32.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Minami's on her way here.\NLet's sit down and talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:36.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Amusement parks are supposed\Nto be places for fun, not fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the deal, Aki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:40.66,Main,,0,0,0,,She's already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.17,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna tell us all the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be honest with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.67,0:09:52.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go to an attraction\Naside from the haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.01,0:09:59.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm? Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.15,Main,,0,0,0,,We're going to the haunted house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,What did Hideyoshi tell you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.40,0:10:14.53,Main,,0,0,0,,There, girls can jump into their\Nboyfriends' arms as much as they like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.20,Main,,0,0,0,,"Scary Abandoned Hospital!!"\N"Haunted House"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Please sign here before you enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:19.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.50,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a written oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Written oaths are often prepared\Nfor dangerous attractions just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I see. Then this place is that dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.76,Main,,0,0,0,,That sounds fun in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.76,0:10:35.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's see... "Oath. I, Yuuji Sakamoto,\Nwill love Shouko Kirishima as my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:38.64,Main,,0,0,0,,as long as I live and will share\Nmy joys and sorrows with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.60,Main,,0,0,0,,So I swear"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:42.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Here is a pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:44.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's your registered seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Here is the vermilion inkpad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:49.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Is it just me?! Is it just me who\Nthinks this situation is strange?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Under the carbon is a second\Nsheet, a marriage registration form.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.49,0:10:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,You're considerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:57.03,Main,,0,0,0,,No, they aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot Test
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.66,0:11:06.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Please hold my bag for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:10.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't hold it sideways as\Nwhat's inside will fall out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:12.38,Main,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, enjoy this scary\Nexperience full of thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.22,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fire Hydrant"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.81,Main,,0,0,0,,An abandoned hospital\Nconverted into a haunted house, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,It does have an authentic feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.15,0:11:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,...ji
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.19,Main,,0,0,0,,--What's that?\N--...than...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this voice... yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--...ji is more... than... bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,--What's this? Synthesized voice? Or is it Hideyoshi imitating me?\N--...ji is more... than... bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.24,0:11:40.91,Main,,0,0,0,,--Either way, it's not that scary.\N--...ji is more... than... bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.91,0:11:44.75,Main,,0,0,0,,--Either way, it's not that scary.\N--Himeji is more my type than Shouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:45.12,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--Himeji is more my type than Shouko.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.96,Main,,0,0,0,,--Huh?\N--She's got bigger breasts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.96,0:11:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Himeji is more my type than Shouko.\NShe's got bigger breasts, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:54.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}is {\i0}a production full of thrills.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:06.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Although the approach\Nis unusual, this really is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:10.77,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:13.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't jump the gun! This is a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.61,0:12:21.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello there. So, how was it?\NDid it make you want to get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.45,0:12:23.37,Main,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that\Nthat would lead to marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.37,0:12:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,They say that when a man and\Na woman fall into a critical situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.58,0:12:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,they'll be connected by a strong bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,That doesn't work when one of\Nthem {\i1}is {\i0}the threat to the other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:33.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji... It's about lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.63,0:12:37.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. All that running around made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm, attention, customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Uhm, a special lunch show will\Nbe held at the restaurant today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.43,0:12:51.69,Main,,0,0,0,,--We've prepared a special menu
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.23,Main,,0,0,0,,--Oh? A special menu, huh?\N--for those of you with a premium ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:55.11,Main,,0,0,0,,--Well then, we'll show you...\N--Please be sure to come to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,--...to the restaurant.\N--Please be sure to come to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to try the special menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:05.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:08.91,Main,,0,0,0,,That was quite tasty, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Everything tastes good when I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,--Hm?\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.29,0:13:17.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Thank you very much for coming
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:20.17,Main,,0,0,0,,to see our special lunch show today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.17,0:13:24.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, we actually have a\Nhigh school student couple here today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.51,Main,,0,0,0,,who are dating with an eye towards marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:27.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:31.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, we'd like to hold an\Nevent to support those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:36.65,Main,,0,0,0,,It's titled "Kisaragi Grand Park's\NWedding Experience Present Quiz"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yaay! Boom! Boom! Honk! Honk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! My retreat has been cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.78,0:13:45.28,Main,,0,0,0,,If they answer all five questions correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,they'll be able to experience\Nour first-rate wedding package.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:52.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be no problem if they decide\Nthey want to get married at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That'll be a big problem, won't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:57.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, Mr. Yuuji Sakamoto and\NMiss Shouko. Please head to the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.75,0:13:58.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Who'd go there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:14:01.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Wedding experience...\NI'll do my best in the quiz.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:05.18,Main,,0,0,0,,--A dream-like wedding experience!\N--Ahhh! Calm down, Shouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Dammit! I have to avoid this situation somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.72,0:14:10.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start the quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.52,0:14:12.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right! If our answers are wrong...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.89,0:14:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm a guy who used to be called a whiz kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making mistakes on purpose is a piece of cake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's question 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, bring it on! There's{\i0}\N{\i1}no question that I can't...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:26.07,Main,,0,0,0,,When is Mr. Yuuji Sakamoto and\NMiss Shouko's wedding anniversary?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:26.95,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Rumble, rumble, rumble."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:30.83,MainTop,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Strange... I can't understand the question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.12,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:33.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Every day is an anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.71,0:14:33.96,Main,,0,0,0,,"Correct"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.50,Main,,0,0,0,,--Correct! Every day is an anniversary! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:38.96,Main,,0,0,0,,--Ahh! Stop it! I'll die of embarrassment!\N--Correct! Every day is an anniversary! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.96,0:14:40.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Here's question 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit! Now that it's come to this,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'll give them a wrong answer at any cost!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:47.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are you going hold your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.01,0:14:48.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Mackerel cooked in {\i1}miso{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.51,0:14:48.76,Main,,0,0,0,,"Correct"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.97,0:14:52.02,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:54.81,Main,,0,0,0,,It is planned that your wedding\Nwill be held in the Phoenix Hall,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:59.07,Main,,0,0,0,,also known as "Mackerel cooked\Nin {\i1}miso{\i0}," at Kisaragi Grand Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait! You definitely named\Nit that just now, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.11,0:15:03.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, here's question 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:05.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I get your way of doing things here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.90,0:15:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll give them an unmistakably{\i0}\N{\i1}wrong answer next.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.45,0:15:11.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you two meet the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:13.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:15.29,Main,,0,0,0,,"Eye"\N"Eye"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.83,0:15:17.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.92,0:15:19.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.29,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those damn jerks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that it's come to this, I'll ignore{\i0}\N{\i1}the question in the middle and answer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.55,0:15:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, here's question 4! The two of yo--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't kno--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:30.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's no use...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.72,0:15:34.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As things stand, I can't give them{\i0}\N{\i1}a wrong answer no matter what I do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.35,0:15:34.64,Main,,0,0,0,,"End"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:36.06,Main,,0,0,0,,"End"\N{\i1}Is this it for me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't it unfair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:43.78,Main,,0,0,0,,We're planning to get married, too.\NWhy are you treating only him special?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:45.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let us do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:48.53,Main,,0,0,0,,"Arrival"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.53,0:15:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Burger hea-- I mean, sir.\NWe're still in the middle of the even--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you idiot! I am a
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,cu-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.37,Main,,0,0,0,,st-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:55.12,Main,,0,0,0,,om-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:55.96,Main,,0,0,0,,er
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.62,Main,,0,0,0,,too, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:16:02.63,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to have the Wedding\NExperience, too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:04.09,Main,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:08.51,Main,,0,0,0,,We're saying that we're\Ngonna participate! Do as we say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll ask a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.80,0:16:17.06,Main,,0,0,0,,If they give us the correct answer,\Nthey'll win. If they're wrong, we'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.06,0:16:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-You can't just...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:21.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my chance! If they're asking{\i0}\N{\i1}us a question, I can definitely give them{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a wrong answer and escape{\i0}\N{\i1}from the Wedding Experience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:25.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:29.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, here's the question. Listen good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the capital city of Europe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:42.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Congratulations! We'll give\NMr. Yuuji Sakamoto and Miss Shouko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:47.22,Main,,0,0,0,,a gift, "Wedding Experience\Nat Kisaragi Grand Park"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.93,0:16:55.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, we'll finally start today's\Nmain event, the Wedding Experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:17:00.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Everyone! First, please\Nwelcome the groom with a big hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,You bastards! I'm seriously\Ngonna kick your ass later!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:11.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll read off his profile...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:13.99,Main,,0,0,0,,This is just an experience and it's\Ntoo much work, so we'll just omit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:18.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Well then, finally, the\Nbride is making her entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:40.06,Main,,0,0,0,,How beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.61,0:17:45.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Er?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.57,0:17:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Do I look like a bride?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:51.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, you look fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:54.82,Main,,0,0,0,,At least, you don't look like a broom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.82,0:17:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.96,0:18:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.38,Main,,0,0,0,,This was... my dream all this time, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.30,0:18:11.80,Main,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream since childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:16.22,Main,,0,0,0,,to have a wedding with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,to become your bride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:23.39,Main,,0,0,0,,The dream I could never\Nmake happen all by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:26.44,Main,,0,0,0,,The dream that I've had since childhood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:29.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So I'm really happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:33.90,Main,,0,0,0,,to be here with my one and only Yuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.37,0:18:43.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Ahh... This is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.54,Main,,0,0,0,,This is, like, really boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care about your love life\Nstories. So hurry up and get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.51,Main,,0,0,0,,We've got stuff to do, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:56.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough with the needless\Nstuff, get to the point already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,In any case, she said it was\Nher dream to become a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.43,0:19:03.27,Main,,0,0,0,,It's like, "how old are you?"\NTo put it bluntly, isn't it creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're playing a gag?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Seriously, it's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:12.28,Main,,0,0,0,,What'd you say, you bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:16.66,Main,,0,0,0,,How dare you say such a thing to\NKirishima! Step outside, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:18.58,Main,,0,0,0,,No, Yoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.58,0:19:21.12,Main,,0,0,0,,The event will be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:22.29,Main,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:24.71,Main,,0,0,0,,--Calm down, Yoshii!\N--...for Kirishima's sake, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:31.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Yoshii! Did you find Kirishima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.06,0:19:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't see her this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:47.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.94,0:19:49.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Where did Kirishima go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.07,0:19:51.07,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't you have some idea?\NWe have to find her quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:59.12,Main,,0,0,0,,It's too much work.\NI wanna go to the bathroom, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.12,0:20:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm in a hurry, so see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:09.13,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a kinda shabby wedding.\NTo put it bluntly, isn't that impossible?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.13,0:20:12.09,Main,,0,0,0,,My dream... is to become a bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.09,0:20:14.42,Main,,0,0,0,,How's that? Do I sound like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.34,0:20:18.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do! That's too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.80,0:20:20.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:21.39,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:23.18,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not really a big deal, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:26.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.93,0:20:30.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me have a word with you, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.16,0:20:42.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.45,0:20:45.83,Main,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Shouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.08,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:52.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:53.46,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:56.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Is my dream... strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:21:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Shouko, let me take this\Nopportunity and tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:06.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Your feelings towards me are a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:11.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Seven years ago, I was stupid\Nand dragged you into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:14.65,Main,,0,0,0,,At that time, I was only trying\Nto take responsibility. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Because of me, you wasted\Nyour years on this worthless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.45,0:21:25.91,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuu... ji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.75,0:21:31.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't laugh at your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.84,Main,,0,0,0,,You picked the wrong man to have feelings for,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.84,0:21:38.30,Main,,0,0,0,,but I think that continuing to care\Nabout one person for a long time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.30,0:21:40.09,Main,,0,0,0,,is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:44.26,Main,,0,0,0,,So your dream is a wonderful\None that you can be proud of
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.26,0:21:46.51,Main,,0,0,0,,and that is second to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,That is, if you don't pick the wrong man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.48,0:21:55.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, it was a rare experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:58.23,Main,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't hurt to bring a souvenir home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:21:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.44,0:22:01.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:06.41,Main,,0,0,0,,the lunch you made... was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.29,0:22:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go home! If we're late,\Npeople will get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:13.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:14.88,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.88,0:22:20.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I... I knew it. I wasn't wrong in the least!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd have to say the first kiss{\i0}\N{\i1}tastes like strawberry milk{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:50.58,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As it turns to evening,{\i0}\N{\i1}I'm pushing my bike home{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.58,0:22:57.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So which is it, a delusion,{\i0}\N{\i1}a simulation, or a dream?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:05.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After stumbling seven times,{\i0}\N{\i1}I stumble an eighth time, wahahaha{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.22,0:23:12.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Each day is different and{\i0}\N{\i1}every day is an anniversary{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.39,0:23:19.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's connect them together to that sky{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:26.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My future is bright. Do I see{\i0}\N{\i1}myself becoming someone big?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.95,0:23:38.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomorrow too, for sure...{\i0}\N{\i1}it'll be sunny, with occasional smiles{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.22,0:23:53.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Question 8.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:56.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What does "computer" refer{\i0}\N{\i1}to in the Japanese language?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.73,0:23:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Super electronic brain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That sounds pretty tough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:03.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next Episode! "Loss of Control, Labyrinths,{\i0}\N{\i1}and the Avatar Instrumentality Project"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.78,0:24:06.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This will be on the test.{\i0}
